39:20.400 --> 39:22.084
- He didn't say that.
-Who's asking you?

39:22.160 --> 39:23.161
Eh.

39:24.640 --> 39:26.324
Write it down.

39:26.400 --> 39:28.767
It's all right. Come on.

39:28.840 --> 39:30.330
Alfie's an old friend.

39:32.800 --> 39:34.290
My friend.

39:35.680 --> 39:37.250
Now, admit it,

39:38.000 --> 39:41.368
